				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Ch%C3%A2n-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-huy%E1%BB%87n-Cao-M%E1%BA%A1i-t%E1%BB%95ng-B%C3%A1c-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-x%C3%A3-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-qu%E1%BA%ADn-c%C3%B4ng-bi-v%C4%83n/poem-OHMF-SMTUy8SSs3daJWY0Q">Chân Định huyện, Cao Mại tổng, Bác Trạch xã Phạm quận công bi văn - 真定縣高邁總博澤社范郡公碑文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/C%E1%BB%95-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-0_CUVjl6d-fPFh6PaPQM6A">Cổ miếu - 古廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/Nam-%C3%94ng-m%E1%BB%99ng-l%E1%BB%A5c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-fyhCR98oGwWB23vOD9LFiw">Nam Ông mộng lục tự - 南翁夢錄序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/author-_vSGbKXOej4AgRYmpqgykw">Hồ Nguyên Trừng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-C%C6%A1/Nh%C3%A3n-nhi-m%E1%BB%8B-Thu-khu%C3%AA/poem-X-40K1XlrcoKqxDGwb5eHg">Nhãn nhi mị - Thu khuê - 眼兒媚－秋閨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-C%C6%A1/author-oVwYIEYCT983JTs6qs8v3A">Lưu Cơ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ph%E1%BB%8Dc-nhung-nh%C3%A2n/poem-2NYSpqJiCjEUIB2gsgV6qA">Phọc nhung nhân - 縛戎人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-Anh/Phong-nh%E1%BA%ADp-t%C3%B9ng/poem-f7joXguQ9pfBkj3BS9TYug">Phong nhập tùng - 風入松</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-Anh/author-to-UkdFjJeg6pwDSfG5oNA">Ngô Văn Anh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Thi%E1%BB%81u-Ch%C3%A2u-V%C4%83n-Hi%E1